public class AckleyFunctionCEC20XXShifted
extends java.lang.Object
implements FunctionIntf

The Ackley test function for real function optimization for up to 1000 dimensions shifted according to the specs in CEC2008. The function's args are usually constrained in the interval [-32, +32]^n. See the tests.AckleyFunction class documentation for the definition of the original function.
